{"tid":1864484,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[號召]各位有多過一個月分量口罩嘅連登仔幫手！","createTime":"2020-02-05T15:31:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T10:54:37.000Z","uid":318876,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5d5e69aed300ebdbb113eefb11fd7e67d5a3ce14","tid":1864484,"uid":318876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T15:31:26.000Z","msg":"請大家出街要帶多兩三個<br />\n見到身邊個無載就送一個比佢<br />\n因為我發現好多人都有要事要出門<br />\n但又無口罩<br />\n尤其是係老人家<br />\n佢地根本無能力排三四個鐘口罩<br />\n好需要大家幫手！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就算對方係咩都好<br />\n少一個人中招<br />\n大家患武漢肺炎嘅風險就越低<br />\n如果到時隻病毒基因特變<br />\n變咗做超級病毒就有口罩都冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過重點都係：封關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39a39d6174b7d594d42a1efa4f362777787eb20a","tid":1864484,"uid":63513,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T15:43:31.000Z","msg":"其實有冇方法group到一批口罩拎出去派<br />\n每人夾十個出黎比人應該都好夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dff4fd562dda2c2bd99e02e3f08e28eea42d3ece","tid":1864484,"uid":32437,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T15:50:46.000Z","msg":"有班廢中廢老見有免費野就死搶爛搶 唔想手足損己去幫呢種仆街"},{"pid":"fb3a8af202d12494dc70a6c30f91714af9983390","tid":1864484,"uid":62514,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T15:53:17.000Z","msg":"廢老不了"},{"pid":"b871a35d3f584a442c27bdb327fe666446ad1525","tid":1864484,"uid":230416,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T15:57:00.000Z","msg":"按照而家情況嚟睇，如果得兩個月存貨都危危地，一個月更加唔洗講，當然有兩個月以上嘅可以捐少少，屋企存貨多到可以賣嘅話，不如考慮一部分用良心價轉賣，一部分送畀真正有需要嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"269201ca0c174ade5594bd3783bf5058c4c2feb8","tid":1864484,"uid":230416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb3a8af202d12494dc70a6c30f91714af9983390","